Madam Cama Road, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: - Department of Law & Justice, Office Order Serial Number, Date 06.02.2025
Department of Law & Justice (itself) Assistant Public Information under the Office Order in Reference for Mumbai Office

Officers, Public Information Officers and First Appellate Authority have been declared. Now for the office of Principal Secretary and Legal Advisor, Principal Secretary and Senior Legal Advisor and Secretary (Law), the following are being declared as Assistant Public Information Officer, Public Information Officer and Appellate Authority.

The Public Information Officer during the period of leave of the above-declared Public Information Officer Ka-2A shall be the Cell Officer (Ka-2). Also, the Deputy Secretary (Ka-2A) shall be the first appellate authority during the period of leave of the First Appellate Authority Under Secretary (Ka-2A).
The Government Order was made available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
